<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화평하다 [화평하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peaceful; harmonious</dd><br>
<dd>마음속이나 사람들 사이에 갈등이 없이 평화롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being mentally peaceful or living at peace with others without any conflict.</dd><br>
<dd>2. peaceful; harmonous</dd><br>
<dd>나라 사이에 충돌이나 전쟁이 없이 평화롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>Two or more countries being at peace with each other without any conflict or war.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화목하다 [화모카다]</dt><br>
<dd>harmonious; concordant; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>서로 뜻이 맞고 정답다.</dd><br>
<dd>Agreeing with each other and being friendly toward each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화기애애하다 [화기애애하다]</dt><br>
<dd>harmonious; amicable; friendly; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>따뜻하고 화목한 분위기가 가득하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An atmosphere being warm and harmonious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평화스럽다 [평화스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없이 조용하고 화목한 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being free from worries or troubles, looking quiet and harmonious.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평화롭다 [평화롭따]</dt><br>
<dd>peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없이 조용하고 화목한 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking quiet and harmonious, free from worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평탄하다 [평탄하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. even; flat</dd><br>
<dd>바닥이 고르고 넓다.</dd><br>
<dd>A floor being even and spacious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calm; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 편하고 조용하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind being comfortable and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smooth; favorable</dd><br>
<dd>일이 미리 생각한 대로 잘되어 나가다.</dd><br>
<dd>A project, etc., being in smooth progress, as planned.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평정하다 [평정하다]</dt><br>
<dd>composed; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없고 고요하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being serene without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평안하다 [평안하다]</dt><br>
<dd>peaceful; not ill</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없다. 또는 무사히 잘 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having no worries or troubles, or being well, healthy and safe.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평강하다 [평강하다]</dt><br>
<dd>peaceful; not ill</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없다. 또는 무사히 잘 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having no worries or troubles, or being well, healthy, and safe.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편하다 [편하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. comfortable; easy; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 괴롭지 않고 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's body or mind being good, neither sick, nor troubled.</dd><br>
<dd>2. handy; easy; simple; convenient</dd><br>
<dd>쉽고 간편하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being easy and simple.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태평하다 [태평하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>나라가 안정되어 아무 걱정이나 탈이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>A nation being peaceful without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tranquil</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 아무 걱정이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind being serene without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
